1
00:00:36,564 --> 00:00:40,902
JULAI 2007, MUSIM PANAS KE LAPAN BELAS

2
00:01:02,590 --> 00:01:04,259
<i>Awak sibuk Sabtu depan?</i>

3
00:01:19,107 --> 00:01:22,068
<i>Nak habiskan masa bersama?
Awak tak boleh tolak.</i>

4
00:01:48,136 --> 00:01:49,345
<i>Okey.</i>

5
00:01:57,562 --> 00:02:00,607
Sol-i, awak dah ada rancangan
untuk Sabtu depan?

6
00:02:00,690 --> 00:02:03,193
Ada konsert Dream. Nak pergi sama?

7
00:02:05,153 --> 00:02:09,073
Maaf. Hari itu saya akan
saksikan perlawanan MU.

8
00:02:09,157 --> 00:02:10,241
Dengan Heon.

9
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:13,620
Apa? Awak dah beli tiket?

10
00:02:13,703 --> 00:02:16,414
Saya boleh beli tiket
pada bila-bila masa, bukan?

11
00:02:16,915 --> 00:02:18,208
Awak ingat MU kelab sekolah?

12
00:02:18,291 --> 00:02:20,210
Tentu semua tiket dah habis dijual.

13
00:02:20,293 --> 00:02:23,588
Sol-i, awak tahu tentang pasukan MU?

14
00:02:23,671 --> 00:02:25,757
Tahu. Pasukan Park Ji-sung.

15
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,967
Heon peminat setia MU.

16
00:02:28,051 --> 00:02:30,136
Ini peluang keemasan.

17
00:02:30,845 --> 00:02:32,513
Aduhai, terharu sungguh.

18
00:02:33,306 --> 00:02:35,767
Harga tiket haram tentu mahal juga.

19
00:02:40,396 --> 00:02:41,773
Dah bersih.

20
00:02:42,357 --> 00:02:45,109
Mak.

21
00:02:45,902 --> 00:02:48,947
Saya dah selesai kemas rumah.

22
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:50,698
Boleh beri duit poket?

23
00:02:53,117 --> 00:02:54,285
Nah.

24
00:02:54,911 --> 00:02:56,496
Berilah lebih lagi.

25
00:02:56,579 --> 00:02:59,916
Saya dah kemas ruang tamu
dan bilik saya dengan bersih.

26
00:02:59,999 --> 00:03:01,751
Berapa yang kamu perlukan?

27
00:03:03,711 --> 00:03:05,171
Nak 100,000 won?

28
00:03:05,254 --> 00:03:07,966
Kamu mengemas selama 10 minit,
tapi minta 100,000 won?

29
00:03:08,049 --> 00:03:09,509
Jangan harap.

30
00:03:11,135 --> 00:03:15,306
Minggu depan MU akan datang ke Seoul.

31
00:03:15,390 --> 00:03:17,517
Saya nak ke perlawanan itu.

32
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:19,769
Park Ji-sung akan turun padang juga.

33
00:03:20,353 --> 00:03:23,147
Saya ingin saksikan
perlawanan bersejarah itu.

34
00:03:23,231 --> 00:03:25,900
Tonton saja di TV. Kita ada TV.

35
00:03:25,984 --> 00:03:28,069
Mak…

36
00:03:37,328 --> 00:03:39,914
Kenapa? Saya terlalu kacak?

37
00:03:41,666 --> 00:03:43,084
Awak tak tengok cermin?

38
00:03:43,167 --> 00:03:45,211
Sudahlah. Berapa duit simpanan awak?

39
00:03:46,629 --> 00:03:50,133
Ha-young, awak tak boleh ugut
secara terang-terangan.

40
00:03:50,216 --> 00:03:51,509
Beritahu saja berapa duit awak.

41
00:03:51,592 --> 00:03:53,761
Kita perlu beli hadiah Sol-i.

42
00:03:54,595 --> 00:03:56,597
Hari jadi Sol-i? Bila?

43
00:03:56,681 --> 00:03:57,890
Sabtu depan.

44
00:03:58,391 --> 00:04:00,852
Apa ini? Kenapa saya tak tahu?

45
00:04:00,935 --> 00:04:05,356
Kami risau kalau awak tahu
awak akan hadiahkan dia sebuah bangunan.

46
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:07,859
Ha-young, serahkan saja kepada Dae-sung

47
00:04:07,942 --> 00:04:09,819
dan tak perlu beli hadiah.

48
00:04:09,902 --> 00:04:10,945
Teruk betul.

49
00:04:11,029 --> 00:04:12,989
Kita kawan dia.

50
00:04:16,326 --> 00:04:19,412
Nah. Ini duit poket saya untuk bulan ini.

51
00:04:19,495 --> 00:04:22,582
Dengan duit awak,
tentu cukup untuk beli tiket MU, bukan?

52
00:04:22,665 --> 00:04:24,042
Tiket MU?

53
00:04:24,125 --> 00:04:26,961
Hei, jangan menyibuk.
Fokus pada pertandingan awak esok.

54
00:04:27,503 --> 00:04:30,506
Kami akan sokong awak.
Awak perlu dapat pingat emas.

55
00:04:30,590 --> 00:04:32,675
Awak tak perlu risau.

56
00:04:32,759 --> 00:04:33,843
Jumpa esok.

57
00:04:34,552 --> 00:04:36,054
- Selamat berlatih.
- Okey.

58
00:04:36,137 --> 00:04:37,221
Selamat berlatih.

59
00:04:39,390 --> 00:04:42,185
Hei, kawan awak
dah biasa beli tiket, bukan?

60
00:04:42,268 --> 00:04:43,603
Tanyalah dia.

61
00:04:44,437 --> 00:04:45,897
Simpan duit ini.

62
00:04:45,980 --> 00:04:47,231
Apa akan jadi kalau hilang?

63
00:04:49,317 --> 00:04:50,151
Nahas.

64
00:04:51,110 --> 00:04:52,945
KEJOHANAN RENANG KEBANGSAAN

65
00:04:53,029 --> 00:04:55,031
{\an8}WOO DAE-SUNG KEBANGGAAN YUIL,
SEMOGA BERJAYA!

66
00:04:55,114 --> 00:04:57,283
{\an8}Jika menang, dia jadi juara kebangsaan?

67
00:04:57,367 --> 00:04:58,618
Ya, betul.

68
00:04:59,243 --> 00:05:01,621
Ha-young, saya sangat gementar.

69
00:05:01,704 --> 00:05:03,664
Saya tak sanggup nak tengok.

70
00:05:03,748 --> 00:05:05,917
Pergi keluar. Jangan ganggu kami.

71
00:05:06,626 --> 00:05:08,503
Itu Woo Dae-sung!

72
00:05:09,337 --> 00:05:13,966
- Woo Dae-sung!
- Woo Dae-sung!

73
00:05:14,050 --> 00:05:15,051
<i>Sedia.</i>

74
00:05:39,826 --> 00:05:40,785
WOO DAE-SUNG TERUNGGUL!

75
00:05:48,126 --> 00:05:49,168
Okey! Sikit lagi!

76
00:05:49,252 --> 00:05:50,670
Woo Dae-sung, awak boleh!

77
00:05:53,631 --> 00:05:55,424
Berjaya!

78
00:06:01,222 --> 00:06:02,098
1. WOO DAE-SUNG

79
00:06:02,181 --> 00:06:05,268
Dia di tempat pertama! Juara!

80
00:06:12,859 --> 00:06:14,026
Itu Dae-sung!

81
00:06:15,069 --> 00:06:16,737
WOO DAE-SUNG KEBANGGAAN YUIL,
SEMOGA BERJAYA!

82
00:06:16,821 --> 00:06:19,365
Atlet Woo, tahniah atas kejayaan awak.

83
00:06:19,448 --> 00:06:20,908
Terima kasih.

84
00:06:20,992 --> 00:06:23,327
Awak tewas
di Kejohanan Piala Presiden yang lepas,

85
00:06:23,411 --> 00:06:25,371
tapi berjaya bangkit semula.

86
00:06:25,454 --> 00:06:28,958
Awak berjaya atasi ujian
dan bangkit semula. Apa rahsia awak?

87
00:06:29,917 --> 00:06:30,793
Semuanya

88
00:06:31,836 --> 00:06:32,962
kerana dia.

89
00:06:36,257 --> 00:06:39,177
Awak ingin umumkan
yang awak ada teman wanita?

90
00:06:39,260 --> 00:06:40,845
Tolong jelaskan lebih lanjut.

91
00:06:41,846 --> 00:06:44,807
Semuanya kerana awak, Sol-i.

92
00:06:44,891 --> 00:06:47,268
{\an8}Hebatnya. Kamu berdua bercinta?

93
00:06:51,355 --> 00:06:52,356
<i>Kawan, makanlah.</i>

94
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:57,361
Tengok ini. Woo Dae-sung dan Shin Sol-i.

95
00:06:57,445 --> 00:06:58,905
Kenapa kamu berdua rapat?

96
00:06:58,988 --> 00:07:01,782
Betulkah kamu berdua sedang bercinta?

97
00:07:01,866 --> 00:07:04,535
Sejak bila?
Siapa yang luahkan perasaan dulu?

98
00:07:04,619 --> 00:07:07,163
Bila kamu berdua
akan umumkan secara rasmi?

99
00:07:07,246 --> 00:07:09,332
Saya tak sabar nak tahu.

100
00:07:09,415 --> 00:07:10,291
Duduk!

101
00:07:10,374 --> 00:07:12,460
Kenapa? Tak bolehkah saya bertanya?

102
00:07:12,543 --> 00:07:13,794
Aduh!

103
00:07:15,796 --> 00:07:16,797
Awak okey?

104
00:07:17,632 --> 00:07:19,342
- Se-hyeong, awak…
- Maaf.

105
00:07:20,218 --> 00:07:21,219
Heon!

106
00:07:22,220 --> 00:07:24,680
- Kenapa?
- Awak baliklah dulu.

107
00:07:24,764 --> 00:07:26,182
Saya ada hal lain.

108
00:07:26,265 --> 00:07:28,518
Kita jumpa Sabtu nanti.

109
00:07:30,228 --> 00:07:31,812
Itu Sol-i punya.

110
00:07:31,896 --> 00:07:34,023
- Encik.
- Selamat datang.

111
00:07:35,983 --> 00:07:39,111
Aduhai. Kami dah ambil pekerja sambilan.

112
00:07:39,195 --> 00:07:40,321
{\an8}Yakah?

113
00:07:40,404 --> 00:07:41,989
{\an8}Encik, sebotol <i>soju</i> di sini.

114
00:07:42,073 --> 00:07:43,616
{\an8}Baiklah.

115
00:07:45,326 --> 00:07:47,745
- Sebotol, ya.
- Okey.

116
00:07:49,288 --> 00:07:52,208
Ini dua set burger <i>bulgogi</i>.

117
00:07:52,291 --> 00:07:53,751
Terima kasih.

118
00:07:54,460 --> 00:07:56,128
Hei, kawan!

119
00:07:56,212 --> 00:07:58,464
Woo Dae-sung!

120
00:08:00,049 --> 00:08:02,510
Apa awak buat sampai tak sempat makan?

121
00:08:02,593 --> 00:08:03,970
Awak patut makan di rumah.

122
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:07,014
Saya gagal cari kerja sambilan

123
00:08:07,098 --> 00:08:09,141
dan tersangat lapar.

124
00:08:09,225 --> 00:08:11,060
Awak buat kerja sambilan di sini?

125
00:08:12,061 --> 00:08:13,437
Seronoknya.

126
00:08:13,521 --> 00:08:15,231
Kenapa nak buat kerja sambilan?

127
00:08:15,314 --> 00:08:17,024
Saya nak beli sesuatu.

128
00:08:18,609 --> 00:08:22,071
Oh, ya. Saya nak tanya awak sesuatu.

129
00:08:22,154 --> 00:08:23,447
Apa dia?

130
00:08:24,156 --> 00:08:27,493
Awak tulis apa
ketika Permainan Cakap Benar itu?

131
00:08:32,248 --> 00:08:33,332
Saya…

132
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:35,710
Itu…

133
00:08:37,753 --> 00:08:41,340
Burger! Saya tulis,
"Saya sangat suka burger."

134
00:08:41,424 --> 00:08:43,843
Yakah? Awak tak tipu?

135
00:08:43,926 --> 00:08:46,012
Tentulah.

136
00:08:47,555 --> 00:08:48,556
Okey.

137
00:08:51,100 --> 00:08:52,101
Terima kasih.

138
00:08:57,231 --> 00:08:58,232
Heon!

139
00:09:01,652 --> 00:09:04,697
Sebenarnya saya nak beri Sabtu nanti.

140
00:09:10,161 --> 00:09:12,538
Tengok! Baju dengan autograf Park Ji-sung.

141
00:09:13,122 --> 00:09:15,207
Saya nak tonton perlawanan dengan awak.

142
00:09:15,291 --> 00:09:17,168
Tapi tiket dah habis jadi saya beli ini.

143
00:09:17,752 --> 00:09:19,170
Simpan saja.

144
00:09:20,421 --> 00:09:22,882
Kenapa? Awak peminat Park Ji-sung.

145
00:09:22,965 --> 00:09:24,258
Tak perlu.

146
00:09:28,679 --> 00:09:31,015
Susah payah saya dapatkan baju ini.

147
00:09:31,515 --> 00:09:34,060
- Saya minta bantuan Dae-sung…
- Berapa?

148
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,480
Lima puluh ribu won.

149
00:09:45,071 --> 00:09:47,198
Puas hati? Jangan ikut saya lagi.

150
00:09:48,115 --> 00:09:49,825
Saya takkan datang Sabtu nanti.

151
00:09:50,534 --> 00:09:51,452
Jangan tunggu.

152
00:10:26,654 --> 00:10:27,988
Jin-hwan, mari sini.

153
00:10:33,828 --> 00:10:35,037
Kenapa mengelak?

154
00:10:35,621 --> 00:10:38,040
- Taklah.
- Awak sedang mengelak.

155
00:10:38,124 --> 00:10:39,083
Pandang saya.

156
00:10:39,166 --> 00:10:40,459
Taklah.

157
00:10:40,543 --> 00:10:44,046
Aduh! Awak terlalu berkilauan,
sebab itu saya tak boleh pandang.

158
00:10:44,922 --> 00:10:47,007
Berhenti bergurau. Cakap, apa dia?

159
00:10:47,967 --> 00:10:49,301
Tentang itu…

160
00:10:50,594 --> 00:10:51,637
Sebenarnya…

161
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:54,557
Dah hilang.

162
00:10:56,225 --> 00:10:58,853
Biar betul? Macam mana boleh hilang?

163
00:10:58,936 --> 00:11:02,189
Ha-young, maafkan saya.
Tapi lebih tepat lagi,

164
00:11:02,273 --> 00:11:04,024
- ia dirampas…
- Betul.

165
00:11:04,608 --> 00:11:05,860
Kita perlu rancangan baru.

166
00:11:17,913 --> 00:11:19,081
Ada apa?

167
00:11:19,165 --> 00:11:20,124
Heon,

168
00:11:20,207 --> 00:11:23,294
awak tahu Sol-i sedang cuba beli
tiket perlawanan MU?

169
00:11:24,128 --> 00:11:26,380
Awak rasa dia buat itu untuk siapa?

170
00:11:27,506 --> 00:11:30,301
Pada hari yang sama ada konsert Dream.

171
00:11:30,384 --> 00:11:32,636
Semua penyanyi kegemaran Sol-i akan hadir.

172
00:11:34,513 --> 00:11:35,431
Hei,

173
00:11:35,514 --> 00:11:37,266
awak tahu Sabtu ini hari jadi Sol-i?

174
00:11:44,356 --> 00:11:45,816
SEKOLAH TINGGI YUIL

175
00:11:51,947 --> 00:11:54,200
SAMA-SAMA KITA WUJUDKAN SEKOLAH BAHAGIA

176
00:11:54,283 --> 00:11:55,409
Helo.

177
00:11:55,493 --> 00:11:56,994
Awak tahu Dae-sung di mana?

178
00:11:58,496 --> 00:12:00,956
Tentang itu…

179
00:12:01,665 --> 00:12:03,584
Pertandingan dah makin dekat.

180
00:12:03,667 --> 00:12:06,420
Tapi dah beberapa hari dia tak berlatih.

181
00:12:07,171 --> 00:12:08,714
Dia pun tak pulang ke rumah.

182
00:12:09,256 --> 00:12:11,467
Encik.

183
00:12:11,550 --> 00:12:13,761
Tolong jangan marah Dae-sung.

184
00:12:13,844 --> 00:12:16,430
Dia amat suka berenang dan sangat baik.

185
00:12:16,514 --> 00:12:20,392
Walaupun dia habiskan masa bersama kami,
dia tak pernah ponteng latihan.

186
00:12:20,476 --> 00:12:22,978
Walaupun seronok
habiskan masa dengan kami,

187
00:12:23,062 --> 00:12:25,147
tapi katanya
dia amat gembira ketika berenang.

188
00:12:27,691 --> 00:12:30,986
Saya rasa Dae-sung
seorang yang amat mengagumkan.

189
00:12:31,695 --> 00:12:33,906
Ini jumlahnya. Cik ingin guna kad?

190
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:38,661
- Ini resit. Terima kasih.
- Sama-sama.

191
00:12:46,502 --> 00:12:47,586
Selamat datang.

192
00:12:48,462 --> 00:12:49,463
Boleh saya…

193
00:12:55,010 --> 00:12:56,470
Satu set burger <i>bulgogi</i>.

194
00:13:01,475 --> 00:13:02,309
Terima kasih.

195
00:13:44,518 --> 00:13:45,644
Hari ini

196
00:13:46,395 --> 00:13:47,896
baliklah ke rumah.

197
00:14:13,464 --> 00:14:14,923
Hei, siapa itu?

198
00:14:15,007 --> 00:14:16,800
- Apa?
- Siapa itu?

199
00:14:18,385 --> 00:14:19,678
Dia…

200
00:14:25,976 --> 00:14:26,977
Ayah saya.

201
00:14:49,625 --> 00:14:50,834
Jin-hwan.

202
00:14:52,294 --> 00:14:53,295
Saya…

203
00:14:55,047 --> 00:14:56,799
Awak tahu di mana nak beli…

204
00:14:58,133 --> 00:14:59,385
tiket konsert Dream?

205
00:14:59,885 --> 00:15:02,638
HEON

206
00:15:11,021 --> 00:15:12,356
<i>Helo?</i>

207
00:15:13,315 --> 00:15:14,733
Apa menu esok?

208
00:15:14,817 --> 00:15:17,444
- Apa?
<i>- Menu waktu rehat esok.</i>

209
00:15:19,113 --> 00:15:20,990
Nasi kari ayam.

210
00:15:21,699 --> 00:15:23,158
Kenapa?

211
00:15:23,242 --> 00:15:26,078
Saya saja nak tahu.

212
00:15:26,161 --> 00:15:28,831
Begitu.

213
00:15:28,914 --> 00:15:30,124
<i>Selamat malam.</i>

214
00:15:30,708 --> 00:15:31,667
<i>Jumpa esok.</i>

215
00:15:48,308 --> 00:15:50,811
Ini tak bermakna saya dah tak marah lagi.

216
00:15:55,524 --> 00:15:56,900
Anak ayah,

217
00:15:56,984 --> 00:15:58,360
cuba teka apa ayah bawa?

218
00:15:59,862 --> 00:16:02,448
Nah! Dua tiket!

219
00:16:02,531 --> 00:16:04,575
Biar betul?

220
00:16:04,658 --> 00:16:07,161
Kenapa kamu tak nampak teruja?

221
00:16:07,244 --> 00:16:09,079
Taklah.

222
00:16:09,163 --> 00:16:11,582
Apa pun, terima kasih, ayah.

223
00:16:18,005 --> 00:16:19,006
Sol-i.

224
00:16:19,673 --> 00:16:20,632
Apa?

225
00:16:23,385 --> 00:16:24,386
Hai.

226
00:16:25,345 --> 00:16:27,848
Hai.

227
00:16:41,361 --> 00:16:42,780
Kawan, hai.

228
00:16:42,863 --> 00:16:44,031
Hai.

229
00:16:45,282 --> 00:16:46,909
Awak dah balik ke rumah, bukan?

230
00:16:46,992 --> 00:16:49,870
Ya, semuanya atas jasa awak. Terima kasih.

231
00:16:49,953 --> 00:16:51,413
Saya kawan yang baik, bukan?

232
00:16:51,497 --> 00:16:54,041
Sudah tentu.
Tak ada kawan yang sebaik awak.

233
00:16:54,625 --> 00:16:56,627
Awak ada hal esok? Jom keluar.

234
00:16:57,586 --> 00:16:59,922
Esok…

235
00:17:01,131 --> 00:17:02,925
- Saya…
- Sol-i.

236
00:17:04,176 --> 00:17:05,385
Apa?

237
00:17:07,596 --> 00:17:08,514
Ada pemadam?

238
00:17:10,641 --> 00:17:12,518
Tunggu. Biar saya cari.

239
00:17:23,779 --> 00:17:24,780
Nah.

240
00:17:27,199 --> 00:17:28,575
Terima kasih.

241
00:17:37,584 --> 00:17:41,797
JELAJAH KOREA MANKHESTE UNITED

242
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:46,718
TIKET

243
00:17:50,347 --> 00:17:52,182
- Helo.
