244
00:17:52,266 --> 00:17:54,518
Saya di depan stadium.

245
00:17:54,601 --> 00:17:55,602
<i>Awak?</i>

246
00:17:56,520 --> 00:17:59,106
Di mana? Saya tak nampak awak.

247
00:17:59,189 --> 00:18:02,025
Saya di pintu utama. Datang ke depan sini.

248
00:18:02,109 --> 00:18:04,236
<i>Perlawanan akan bermula dalam masa sejam.</i>

249
00:18:04,319 --> 00:18:06,697
- "Perlawanan"?
- Ya.

250
00:18:07,322 --> 00:18:09,533
Kita dah janji untuk tonton perlawanan MU.

251
00:18:10,659 --> 00:18:11,743
Okey.

252
00:18:12,578 --> 00:18:13,787
Saya akan ke sana.

253
00:18:21,420 --> 00:18:22,671
Sol-i.

254
00:18:23,630 --> 00:18:25,048
Heon!

255
00:18:26,758 --> 00:18:29,469
Apa? Tiket palsu?

256
00:18:29,553 --> 00:18:33,432
